data.description: Don't miss out on this awesome opportunity to purchase a MOVE IN READY home for under $100,000. To answer your question, no this is not a joke! This home offers two beds in a convenient location just minutes from stores, restaurants and so much more. Close enough to downtown yet far enough to have peace and quiet. With newer windows that are less two years old, this home is extremely efficient. The wooden privacy fence allows you to sit on your back deck to enjoy a nice and quiet evening. Let the showings begin!
